You want directions from 'Airport' to 'Forbes and Murray', leaving now (10 pm). As the assistant gives you the directions, alternate randomly between (i) asking for the next instruction, (ii) asking for more details, and (iii) asking for the next trivia question (start at question 3)

 The AI Assistant can handle:
- Giving trip directions
- Playing trivia
